					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Devin Thomas O’Shea</h4>
												<p>Devin Thomas O’Shea is the author of <em>The Veiled Prophet</em>, publishing with Haymarket Books in 2026. His writing is in <i>The Nation</i>, <i>The Iowa Review</i>, <i>LA Review of Books</i>, <i>Boulevard</i>, and elsewhere. Represented by Erik Hane, Headwater Literary.</p>
